WiPi version 0.01
=================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   $ perl Makefile.PL
   $ make
   $ make test
   $ make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   WiringPi

COPYRIGHT AND LICENCE

The XS-File is free to use. There will be no REAL support for it. 
If you find something not working, please let me know it to fix problems!

